### 2. Component Core (Endpoint Factory)
- **FixComponent.java** — Extends DefaultComponent, manages FixConfiguration, creates FixEndpoint instances

### 3. Endpoint (Message Exchange Factory)
- **FixEndpoint.java** — Extends DefaultEndpoint, creates Consumer and Producer instances, decorated with @UriEndpoint for auto-discovery

### 4. Message Processors
- **FixConsumer.java** — Extends DefaultConsumer, receives inbound FIX messages, manages FIX acceptor sessions
- **FixProducer.java** — Extends DefaultAsyncProducer, sends outbound FIX messages asynchronously

### 5. Module Registration
- **pom.xml (camel-fix)** — Maven POM for the new module
- **components/pom.xml** — Updated to register camel-fix module in alphabetical order

